snippet.title: Warspace 2 Teaser | Space Co-op RPG | Indie Game
snippet.description:
Website: https://Warspace2.com
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1344550?utm_source=YT

Warspace 2 is an open-world, space shooter, indie game with RPG elements, tons of loot and cooperative gameplay. You can trade, craft, and fight your way through a universe, either solo or with a friends in coop.
